                    "alt": "Scions of Domora",
                    "game-obj": "Archetypes",
                    "aonid": 336
                }
            }
        ],
        "prerequisite": "*Familiar Master Dedication*; you have befriended a spirit guide and it bonded with you using its Bond to Mortal ability.",
        "special": "You can take Scion of Domora Dedication even if you have the Familiar Master Dedication and have not taken two other Familiar Master feats. You can\u2019t select another dedication feat until you have gained at least two other feats from the scion of Domora or familiar master archetypes.",
